* v1.1.0    UNRELEASED

- Added new macro ~thread$~.  d87c492

- Macro ~and$~ now accepts more than two arguments, like ~and>~ already
  did.  ~and>~ is now an alias for ~and$~.  Please see its docstring if
  you would like to keep using it.  ee63a74

- Fixed debug declaration of ~when$~ and ~while-let*~.  903a5e3, 680cd26

- Added indentation declaration for ~and$~.  93768a2

* v1.0.0    2026-05-01

First stable release.
